cova.data.taints

Class AbstractTaint

  • java.lang.Object
    • cova.data.taints.AbstractTaint
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ConcreteTaint, SymbolicTaint, ZeroTaint

    public abstract class AbstractTaint
extends Object
    This is the abstract class of taint. A taint must have an access path and a constraint when this taint is alive.
